Hi <%= "#{@reserver.first_name}" %>,

Thank you for booking with OpenPlay!
Your booking details are shown below for your reference:

Booking Number: <%= @order.id %>
Date: <%= present_date_in_weekday_month_day_format(@order.booking_date) %>
Place: <%= @order.booking_place %>
Price: <%= present_booking_price(@order.total_price) %>

Booking Details:
<% @order.bookings.each do |booking| %>
  <%= @order.reservable_type %>: <%= booking.reservable_name %>
  Time: <%= present_range_of_time(booking.start_time, booking.end_time) %>
  # Players: <%= booking.number_of_players %>
  Options:
    <% booking.reservable_options.each do |option| %>
      <%= option.reservable_option_name.humanize %>
    <% end %>
  ------------------------------
<% end %>

Thank you,
The OpenPlay Team
